Nigerian superstar disc jockey, DJ Jimmy Jatt releases the music video for his collaborative tune, “Halima” featuring Mr Eazi and Skales. In the video, Mr Eazi and Skales profess their love for “Halima”. From a cosy bar ambience, the video transitions to a boat cruise where both artists and their love interests join DJ Jimmy Jatt. The video was shot and directed by Director K Rus and Unblvabl Studios. Watch the video for “Halima” below: 